\@writefile{lot}{\contentsline {table}{\numberline {7}{\ignorespaces Wall-clock cost of the full HCCP pipeline and main baselines, single chrom-LOO sweep on TraitGym. CPU times on 16-core Xeon; GPU on a single T4. Memory peak excludes Python overhead. $\hat  {p}$ training is per feature set; $\hat  {\sigma }$ training is on chrom-LOO OOF residuals; Mondrian calibration is reported per $K$. DEGU-lite shares the $\hat  {p}$ backbone. The $B = 200$ chromosome-level bootstrap (Tab.\nobreakspace  {}\ref  {tab:main}) reuses cached calibration scores and adds $\sim 30$ CPU-min total.}}{22}{table.7}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{tab:compute}{{7}{22}{Wall-clock cost of the full HCCP pipeline and main baselines, single chrom-LOO sweep on TraitGym. CPU times on 16-core Xeon; GPU on a single T4. Memory peak excludes Python overhead. $\phat $ training is per feature set; $\shat $ training is on chrom-LOO OOF residuals; Mondrian calibration is reported per $K$. DEGU-lite shares the $\phat $ backbone. The $B = 200$ chromosome-level bootstrap (Tab.~\ref {tab:main}) reuses cached calibration scores and adds $\sim 30$ CPU-min total}{table.7}{}}
